features: REUSABLE ECO-FRIENDLY WRAPPING PAPER FOR GIFTS & PRESENTS: Hawksbill Paper has a fantastic range of brown paper rolls for several uses. This thin paper is an ideal product for wrapping up items for Birthdays, anniversaries, special occasions and Christmas. It also works well as packaging for homemade items from small businesses. It is slightly thicker than standard wrapping paper, meaning this is easy to reuse again to regift, reducing the churn of single-use paper when gift giving.

440MM x 30M KRAFT PAPER FOR PARCELS: This long roll of brown craft paper will cover lots of needs for delivering items in the post such as standard packaging, void fill or interior wrapping. At 80 GSM, this is prime wrapping paper or packaging for items to send via courier. The surface of the paper has a slight texture, making it perfect for sticking labels, stamps and securing with Sellotape.

HANDY FOR KIDS PLAY & CRAFTING TIME: Kraft paper is so great for children as it is thin enough for children to easily cut, stick and fold. Use this paper for several uses such as quick table coverings for messy craft days with the kids. You could also paint directly or draw monsters and fairytales. This would be a handy product to have for school projects also due to its versatility.

MADE FROM 100% RECYCLED PAPER: Our kraft paper rolls have been sustainably sourced and originate from pre-used paper fibres. When the paper is disposed of, this paper can be recycled again, making it a perfect guilt-free option for wrapping gifts, packaging items, protecting surfaces or creating art. Use Hawksbill for sustainable and eco options when it comes to paper.

OVER 90 YEARS’ EXCELLENCE IN THE PAPER TRADE: Hawksbill Paper is an FSC-accredited family business which has been dealing in the UK paper trade for nearly a century. Our company is a mark of true quality paper; we travel worldwide to source the right paper for your home and office needs. We offer a range of A3 and A4 paper products available in many colours, sizes and pack quantities as well as our new poster paper and kraft wrapping paper.
description: From the manufacturer WRAPPING PARCELS, GIFTS OR PACKAGING ALLOW KIDS TO BE CREATIVE MAKING STATIONERY OR TABLE SETTINGS HOBBY, ARTS & CRAFTS Kraft paper in a variety of sizes Hawksbill carries a number of sizes of brown paper rolls to cater to your every need 400mm x 30m single and twin packs 440mm x 30m single and twin packs 500mm x 10m single and twin packs 500mm x 20m single and twin packs 500mm x 50m single and twin packs Hawksbill Card & Craft What is kraft paper? Kraft paper is a smooth and strong brown paper used in commercial and home scenarios. Kraft paper is such a versatile material and is a good item to keep at home. An easy to use paper, this product is suitable for children to cut, stick and paint. As a great eco option, this paper is easy to reuse to wrap parcels or presents for Christmas and other special occasions. It can be used for multiple things such as: Packaging or void filling Present or gift wrapping Arts & crafts, drawing and painting Protecting surfaces while painting Making notice boards
